displayProperties.name: Riven's Wishes IV
displayProperties.description:
Defeat combatants in the Blind Well, located in the Font of Starlight in the Dreaming City. Additionally, complete a Tier III Blind Well activity.

Activating the Blind Well requires Charged Light, which can be earned by completing activities and opening chests within the Dreaming City. Charged Light also is rewarded for completing Petra Venj's bounties.

displayProperties.name: Riven's Wishes V
displayProperties.description:
Complete one of the following objectives:
 
Defeat Taken bosses or minibosses in Rheasilvia within the Dreaming City.
 
OR
 
Summon and defeat Pauurc, the Farseer's Heir, located in Rheasilvia within the Dreaming City.
 
To summon Pauurc, seek out a Farseer Saboteur, claim its Awoken charge, and place it in the appropriate vessel.

displayProperties.name: Riven's Wishes II
displayProperties.description:
Open Ascendant Chests located in the Dreaming City. The Ascendance buff, activated by consuming a Tincture of Queensfoil, is required to access the chests by revealing hidden paths. 

A Tincture of Queensfoil can be acquired by completing activities and bounties throughout the Dreaming City. Tinctures can also be purchased from Petra Venj. Tinctures have no effect outside the boundaries of the Dreaming City.
